The following former Torontos have been inducted into the Hockey Hall of Fame:
* Harry Cameron
* Cy Denneny
* Scotty Davidson
* Frank Foyston
* Hap Holmes
* Duke Keats
* Jack Marshall
* Frank Nighbor
* Reg Noble
* Jack Walker

